  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a multimedia educational computer program
      can increase colorectal cancer screening rates in low and adequate literacy patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Results will be stratified by low/marginal and adequate literacy as determined by the Rapid
      Estimate of Adult Literacy in Medicine instrument.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
